---
---
<section id="top" class="relative isolate overflow-hidden pt-28 pb-20 md:pt-36 md:pb-28">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-radial-fade"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-grid"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-grid-beam"></div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4">
    <div class="grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-12">
      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <a href="#cotizar" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-brand-200 bg-white/70 px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-700 backdrop-blur">
          <span class="grid h-4 w-4 place-items-center rounded-full bg-brand-500 text-[10px] text-white">☀</span>
          Energía solar fotovoltaica
        </a>

        <h1 class="font-display mt-6 text-balance text-5xl font-bold leading-[1.02] tracking-tight text-ink-950 md:text-6xl">
          Convertimos
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-600 to-brand-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent">la luz del sol</span>
          en ahorro y sostenibilidad.
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-6 max-w-xl text-pretty text-lg leading-relaxed text-ink-700">
          Diseñamos e instalamos sistemas solares a la medida de cada cliente:
          residenciales, comerciales e industriales. On-Grid, Off-Grid o híbridos —
          todos con monitoreo inteligente y mantenimiento incluido.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
          <a href="/#contacto" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-brand-600 px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-glow transition hover:bg-brand-700">
            Cotizar mi sistema
            <svg class="h-4 w-4 transition group-hover:translate-x-1" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#beneficios" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-ink-300 bg-white/60 px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-ink-900 backdrop-blur transition hover:border-brand-400 hover:text-brand-700">
            Ver beneficios
          </a>
        </div>

        <dl class="mt-12 grid max-w-md grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div>
            <dt class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-500">Ahorro típico</dt>
            <dd class="font-display mt-1 text-2xl font-bold text-ink-950">60–90%</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-500">Payback</dt>
            <dd class="font-display mt-1 text-2xl font-bold text-ink-950">3–5 años</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-500">Vida útil</dt>
            <dd class="font-display mt-1 text-2xl font-bold text-brand-600">25+ años</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>

      <div class="relative lg:col-span-5">
        <div class="relative mx-auto aspect-[3/4] max-w-md">
          <div class="absolute -inset-6 rounded-[2rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-200/60 to-lime-glow/40 blur-2xl"></div>
          <div class="relative h-full overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-white/60 shadow-glow">
            <img src="/img/solar/solar-wind-farm.jpg" alt="Planta solar Disart Energy" class="h-full w-full object-cover" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" />
            <div class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-1/3 bg-gradient-to-t from-ink-950/80 to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-5 left-5 right-5">
              <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-200">Generando ahora</p>
              <p class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-white">412 kW · 92% rendimiento</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
